    "form_header_text": "Congressman Tom Kean, Jr. (NJ-07): Appropriations Application for FY27",
    "form_instructions_text": "Thank you for your interest in the Fiscal Year 2027 Congressional appropriations process. If you are interested in submitting information pertaining to programmatic or report language requests, please fill out this form as completely as possible for each request that you want considered. This is NOT the appropriate form for Community Project Funding (CPF) requests. To adhere to Appropriations Committee deadlines, electronic copies of this form should be returned no later than the dates listed below. This form will be updated with those dates when those deadlines are announced. There is no guarantee that your request will be supported. Early submissions are welcome and appreciated. For any further questions please contact Dan.Butler@mail.house.gov.",
