            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "YES; Reps. Don Bacon (R-NE) and Judy Chu (D-CA)",
            "rationale": "The reference values confirm an existing House letter led by Reps. Bacon and Chu.",
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "field_id": "microsoft_forms:01:rfd6d41ac513c45e784a7a816431dde47:80c492641ddd",
            "label": "Description of Program Request or Proposed Bill / Report Language. If requesting language, please provide a\u0000complete draft\u0000of your requested language and whether it is bill or report language. If the draft does not fit below, please email this draft to Dan.Butler@mail.house.gov with \"Kean FY27 Requested Report/Bill Language\" in the subject line.",
            "help_text": null,
            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": true,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Programmatic request for $9,000,000,000 for NASA's Science Mission Directorate (SMD)\n* Funding to support a balanced portfolio of missions across Earth Science, Planetary Science, Astrophysics, Heliophysics, and Biological and Physical Sciences\n* Ensures execution of high-priority missions as identified by the National Academies' decadal surveys\n* Provides stability for the specialized aerospace workforce and industrial supply chains necessary for deep-space exploration",
            "rationale": "Directly references the $9B ask and frames it within the SMD's broad portfolio and decadal survey priorities as recommended in the advocacy context.",
            "confidence": "high"
          }
        ]
      },
